\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check the room:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (Despite the years I\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92ve spent here, I keep the place in good shape. There\u8217\'92s a computer I can use to check on my files, and I have some trophies on the walls.)}
