\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check sword display:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (A ceremonial sword from the King, a symbol of my ranking as Just. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s gaudy and not very functional. But it could come in handy in a pinch. Should I take it?)}
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check image file:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (A photo of myself crouched next to a group of orphans from Outer Rim. I used to do city cleanup and ended up saving some from traders.)  }
\par\plain \f0\fs24\b0\i0
\par\plain {\f1\fs24\b0\i1 Check medal:}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0 Zima: (A metal given by my old Chief. It\loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8217\'92s made of bronze and embossed with a charge of the Kingdom, a headless eagle.)}
